OL,3,CWhat next for Sunderland after Michael
OL,4,CBeale sacking?
OL,6,FSunderland are once again on the
OL,7,Flookout for a new permanent head coach
OL,8,Fafter sacking Michael Beale.
OL,10,FThe former Rangers and QPR head
OL,11,Fcoach's appointment was quickly
OL,12,Ffrowned upon by a substantial number
OL,13,Fof Sunderland supporters, following
OL,14,Fthe popularity of former boss Tony
OL,15,FMowbray.
OL,17,FIn the end, he lasted just 63 days.
OL,18,FWinning four of his 12 games in all
OL,19,Fcompetitions before his dismissal,
OL,20,Flosing his last match in charge to
OL,21,FMowbray's new side Birmingham City.
