OL,3,CWhat next for Sunderland after Michael
OL,4,CBeale sacking?
OL,6,FBeale's assistant Mike Dodds will pick
OL,7,Fup the managerial reins until the end
OL,8,Fof the campaign after previously
OL,9,Fleading the club to two wins in three
OL,10,Fgames when Mowbray was unexpectedly
OL,11,Fsacked in December.
OL,13,FThe decision to appoint the 37-year-
OL,14,Fold on an interim basis buys the club
OL,15,Ftime to consider a long-term
OL,16,Freplacement.
OL,18,FAs any manager, Dodds has a task on
OL,19,Fhis hands. And for Beale, it was not
OL,20,Fmeant to be.
