OL,3,CWhat next for Sunderland after Michael
OL,4,CBeale sacking?
OL,6,FA 3-0 defeat at home to Coventry City
OL,7,Fin Beale's first match left many fans
OL,8,Fbelieving their worst fears had
OL,9,Falready been realised and they were
OL,10,Ffurther alienated when he suggested
OL,11,Fthe reason they were yet to take to
OL,12,Fhim was because of his London accent.
OL,14,FA disappointing cup defeat to
OL,15,FNewcastle United did little to win him
OL,16,Fany favour but matters came to a head
OL,17,Fduring Saturday's 2-1 defeat to
OL,18,FBirmingham, three days after being
OL,19,Fbeaten 1-0 by relegation battlers
OL,20,FHuddersfield.
