OL,3,CWhat next for Sunderland after Michael
OL,4,CBeale sacking?
OL,6,FBeale appeared to blank 21-year-old
OL,7,FTrai Hume after the defender's 87th-
OL,8,Fminute substitution, later apologising
OL,9,Fto the Welsh international after
OL,10,Fstating he had not seen him approach.
OL,11,FHowever, the footage quickly
OL,12,Fcirculated on social media with a host
OL,13,Fof theories put forward by Sunderland
OL,14,Ffans.
OL,16,FThe Black Cats squad is made up of a
OL,17,Fstrong core of young talents and hard-
OL,18,Fworking homegrown stars and are
OL,19,Fcapable of playing some of the most
OL,20,Fexciting football in the Championship
OL,21,Fon their day.
