OL,3,CWhat next for Sunderland after Michael
OL,4,CBeale sacking?
OL,6,FIf Dodds can get the players back
OL,7,Fonside and showing the kind of form
OL,8,Fthey did under Mowbray then the smiles
OL,9,Fwill quickly return inside the Stadium
OL,10,Fof Light.
OL,12,FResults will almost certainly follow
OL,13,Fwith plenty still to play for. The
OL,14,Fclub remain firmly within the play-off
OL,15,Fhunt despite the disappointment under
OL,16,FBeale with a gap of four points to
OL,17,Fsixth easily surmountable at this
OL,18,Fstage of the season.
