OL,3,CWhat next for Sunderland after Michael
OL,4,CBeale sacking?
OL,6,FOn-field matters must, and will, take
OL,7,Fprecedence again during the interim
OL,8,Fperiod but the Sunderland hierarchy
OL,9,Fand club's supporters can be forgiven
OL,10,Ffor having half an eye on the
OL,11,Fpermanent appointment.
OL,13,FIt is unclear whether Dodds would like
OL,14,Fthe job full-time but he will never
OL,15,Fhave a better opportunity to prove his
OL,16,Fworth.
