OL,3,CWhat next for Sunderland after Michael
OL,4,CBeale sacking?
OL,6,FMore established names like Steve
OL,7,FCooper, Will Still and Roy Keane are
OL,8,Flikely to be thrown around over the
OL,9,Fcoming months but Dodds has the chance
OL,10,Fto ensure the club cannot look
OL,11,Felsewhere.
OL,13,FHe has 13 games to make his case,
OL,14,Fstarting in front of the home support
OL,15,Fagainst Swansea at the Stadium of
OL,16,FLight on Saturday.
